### RawImage Class (Image Loading)
**Location:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775497559114-1vf7ng/src/utils/image.js` (lines 77-187)

